Make GET request to http://localhost:3000/api/books

POST - Create New Book (30 seconds)
What to Show:

Make POST request to http://localhost:3000/api/books
Set Content-Type header to application/json
Use this body:

json{
  "title": "The Hobbit",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "978-0-547-92822-7",
  "publishedYear": 1937,
  "genre": "Fantasy",
  "pages": 310,
  "language": "English",
  "available": true
}



PUT - Update Book (30 seconds)
What to Show:

Copy the _id from the book you just created
Make PUT request to http://localhost:3000/api/books/{id}
Update the book:

json{
  "title": "The Hobbit (Annotated Edition)",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "978-0-547-92822-7",
  "publishedYear": 1937,
  "genre": "Fantasy",
  "pages": 366,
  "language": "English",
  "available": false
}


DELETE - Remove Book (20 seconds)
What to Show:

Make DELETE request to http://localhost:3000/api/books/{id}
Show 200 OK response: {"message": "Book deleted successfully"}